      <section id="about-us">
        <div class="about">
            <h2 class="heading">What is this all about ?</h2> <br>
            <p class="head-des" class="text">We solve the problem of blood emergencies by connecting <span
                    class="one-line"><br></span> blood donors directly with blood banks in blood need. </p>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="about-col">
                    <div class="image">
                        <img src="./images/drop.png">
                    </div>
                    <h3>What we do ?</h3>
                    <p>We connect blood donors and recipients with blood banks, without any intermediary organizatons such as blood agencies, for an
                      efficient and seamless process and to avoid any delay.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-col">
                    <div class="image">
                        <img src="./images/innovation.png">
                    </div>
                    <br>
                    <h3>Innovative</h3>
                    <p>Blood Care is an innovative approach to address global health.We provide <span>immediate
                            access and contacts</span> to blood banks.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-col">
                    <div class="image">
                        <img src="./images/netwotk.png">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Network</h3>
                    <p>Blood Care, currently a mini-project, could be one of several community organizations in future, working to
                        respond to emergencies in an efficient manner.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-col">
                    <div class="image">
                        <img src="./images/noti.png">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Get notified</h3>
                    <p>Blood Care is made to connect network partners with blood donors and recipients through a web based solution.
                      This will increase the ease-of-use and ease-of-access with fast and efficient solution of the blood-shortage problem. 
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-col">
                    <div class="image">
                        <img src="./images/cost.png">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Totally Free</h3>
                    <p>Blood Care's ultimate goal is to provide an easy-to-use, easy-to-access, fast, efficient,
                        and reliable way to donate life-saving blood and get access to it, totally <span>Free of cost.</span></p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-col">
                    <div class="image">
                        <img src="./images/save.png">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Save Life</h3>
                    <p>Blood care is a DBMS Mini-Project aiming at saving lives and our main objective is to make sure that everything is done
                        to protect vulnerable persons.<span>Help
                            us by donating or refering as much as possible</span></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    {{#if result}}
    <section class="volunteer">
      <div class="user-container container" id="vol-sect">
      <div class="title-head">
            <h1 class="title">Our Super Heroes </h1>
        </div>
        <p class="content">We depend on volunteers! Volunteers make up 96% of our total<span class="line"><br></span>
            workforce and carry on our humanitarian work. Blood donation is healthy,<span class="line"><br></span> our
            volunteers are available 24/7 to help and donate
            blood. Blood banks store blood<span class="line"><br></span> bags but our volunteers are there with you in
            an emergency for a blood transfusion real time.</p>
          <ul class="volunt container">
              {{#each result}}
              <form class="vol">
                  <span class=" vol-i index">{{inc @index}}</span>
                  <span class=" vol-i number">{{this.Name}}</span>
                  <span class=" vol-i blood-group">{{this.Bgroup}}<i class="fa fa-tint" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
              </form>
              {{/each}}
          </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
    {{/if}}
